348
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:36,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Alles sehr fein gewürfelt.</font>

349
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:38,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Dann Koriander dazu.</font>

350
00:20:39,720 --> 00:20:42,080
